Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 04 of Thoracic CT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Cardiovascular/Thoracic aorta' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Vasosclerosis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Vascular dilatation' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Vascular dilatation' checkbox
Then 'Ectasia' radio button is enabled
And 'Aneurysm' radio button is enabled
And 'Aortic root' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ascending aorta' checkbox is enabled
And 'Aortic arch' checkbox is enabled
And 'Descending aorta' checkbox is enabled
And 'Maximum diameter' input field is enabled
